rhythmbox-plugin-rhythmremote: rhythmbox-plugin-rhythmremote (Rhythmbox web interface)
rhythmbox-plugin-rhythmremote:
rhythmbox-plugin-rhythmremote: 
rhythmbox-plugin-rhythmremote: The goal of this project is to create a fully functional mobile web-interface
rhythmbox-plugin-rhythmremote: for Rhythmbox. It's implemented as an Rhythmbox plugin written in python. The
rhythmbox-plugin-rhythmremote: plugin starts a local webserver on 0.0.0.0:8001 (or localhost),
rhythmbox-plugin-rhythmremote: which handles the requests of the browser.
